@startuml

actor Student
participant Course
participant Quiz
participant Certificate

== Enrollment ==

Student -> Course : enroll(course)
Course --> Student : enrollment confirmed

== Quiz Attempt ==

Student -> Quiz : startQuiz()
Quiz --> Student : display questions

Student -> Quiz : submit answers
Quiz -> Quiz : evaluate answers

Quiz --> Student : result

== Certificate ==

alt Passed
    Quiz -> Certificate : generate()
    Certificate --> Student : certificate issued
else Failed
    Quiz --> Student : no certificate
end

@enduml